image_analysis.description: A photograph of two actors, a woman and a man, standing next to a large Oscar statuette at what appears to be the Academy Awards. The woman, on the left, is wearing a light-colored, sequined gown and is holding an Oscar. She has her mouth open and is looking at the man. The man, in the center, is wearing a white tuxedo jacket and black bow tie, also holding an Oscar, and is looking down at his jacket. To the right is a large Oscar statuette on a pedestal. There are floral arrangements in the scene. The image has text overlaid at the bottom.
image_analysis.layout: The two individuals are centrally located. A large statuette is on the right. Text is overlaid across the bottom of the image, with a document identifier in the lower-right corner.
